</li>
<li>Chapter 19 Templating with Smarty
</li>
<li>Chapter 20 Web Services
</li>
<li>Chapter 21 Secure PHP Programming
</li>
<li>Chapter 22 SQLite
</li>
<li>Chapter 23 Introducing PDO
</li>
<li>Chapter 24 Building Web Sites for the World
